Package: tidybibliometrics
Title: A package for examining the contents of a bibtex file from ISI or SCOPUS
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Yuyi", "Shen", email = "yuyi.shen3@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A bibliometric analysis package inspired by the bibliometrix package. It provides functions for reading bibliometric data (as a bibtex file) from ISI or Scopus into a tibble, tidying the resulting tibble, and analyzing specific columns of the tibble. The package also provides versions of the aforementioned functions for usage with R Shiny. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
Imports:
  stringr (>= 1.2.0),  
  tibble (>= 1.3.3),
  dplyr (>= 0.7.2)
Suggests:
  visNetwork (>= 2.0.1)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
